race.description: Magic Millions March Yearling Sale C,G&E Handicap (Bm58)
race.comment: LA CACHE A VIN (3) saluted at Grafton two runs ago. Fair effort last time out over 1040m at Grafton in much stronger than this when beaten 3 lengths. The 2kg claim helps offset some of the extra weight allocated and he looks well placed to bounce back. LOVE RAT (4) comes out of the same Grafton contest where he  didn't manage the wide barrier. He was only beaten 1.4L at Grafton at this level prior and that reads well enough. Draws inside today and the 2kg claim benefits as well. SEND A TELEGRAM (6) resumes and missed 1L here first-up last time. Races forward and Bullock's booking is a positive sign. Has ability. SPEEDY TARGET (7) will run along and has a 3kg claim. The tongue tie is on for the first time and he should be ready to hit his straps.
